content: Both my 3 and 6 year olds love this game and it is a great way to stimulate their logic thinking. Sporadically there is an issue however where blocks can no longer be placed where it clearly should be possible to place them. Restarting the level resolves this, but it can be confusing for the kids. Also, some more levels would be great!
It a great game for kids
